title: #70 GIMME YOUR STUFF! Julie Borowski, Ed Morrissey and SooperMexican
description: This week, NotGayJared explains how he systematically signed up for #FightFor15 protests only to discover it was a sham. Noted libertarian, Julie Borowski stops by for a friendly debate, Ed Morrissey explains delegate math and SooperMexican plays "Spot the Tranny!"
